arm, you\'ll maybe even make some friends .. And of course, the beer is very cheap. Open every day of the week it closes at 4am on weekends.\nAddress: Vodièkova 10, Nové Mesto\n\nVoici un bar qui vaut le détour,  à cinq minutes de la Place Wenceslas: le Vinárna U Sudu.\nIl a beau avoir l’allure d’un minuscule bar à vin, vous serez surpris lorsque vous découvrirez ses trésors cachés en sous-sol, pas moins de quatre salles sur différents niveaux! L\'ambiance y est chaleureuse, vous vous y ferez même peut-être quelques amis.. Et bien évidemment, la bière y est très bon marché. Ouvert tous les jours de la semaine, il ferme à 4h du matin en fin de semaine.\nAdresse: Vodièkova 10, Nové Mesto','Vinárna U Sudu','','inherit','open','open','','273-revision-3','','','2010-06-24 23:10:53','2010-06-24 22:10:53','',273,'http://www.nofeeshostels.com/info/273-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(1701,1,'2010-06-24 23:13:51','2010-06-24 22:13:51','<p>If you have the chance, try to escape from the city for the day, by taking a a train ticket (the DART, Dublin Area Rapid Transportation).<br />\r\nFor less than 10 euros, you can use it without limits for 24 hours. The railway takes you to either Dun Laoighre (south) or north to Malahide, two very pleasant coastal cities where you can fill your lungs with fresh sea air! Malahide also has a beautiful castle worth a visit. The small fishing port of Howth is also a nice destination for the day.</p>\r\n','Going out of Dublin for the day','','inherit','open','open','','229-revision-5','','','2010-06-24 23:13:51','2010-06-24 22:13:51','',229,'http://www.nofeeshostels.com/info/229-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(1592,1,'2010-06-24 23:13:48','2010-06-24 22:13:48','If you have the chance, try to escape from the city for the day, by taking a a train ticket (the DART, Dublin Area Rapid Transportation).\r\nFor less than 10 euros, you can use it without limits for 24 hours. The railway takes you to either Dun Laoighre (south) or north to Malahide, two 